plot.content: This plot is one physical counterpart delivered to the digital owner of 'Plottable Golden Train #111'. Plottable Golden Train includes many variations (bridges, cactus, clouds, eagles, colors,...) entirely generated with code at mint (generative art).

prev.content: This is a pen plotted interpretation of this shader work by @naibdian. Fire and Ice ink was so unpredictable and capricious and this goes even more into abstract art. A4 square.
